						               													<description>5150 Fringe Space is about living life on the edge. Sometimes that means salvaging space wrecks, hunting space pirates, or hauling cargo and passengers from one world to the next.&amp;#10;But it also means carousing in a city, rescuing crewmembers from Alien abductors, and fistfights in a low end bar. 5150 Fringe Space is a RPG Lite game that can also be played as a man to man or ship to ship combat game. Inside you&amp;rsquo;ll find:&amp;#10;&amp;#10;A variety of Classes, Attributes, Professions, and Alien Races to make your characters unique.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Man to man combat rules for when you&amp;rsquo;re on a planet.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Ship to ship combat rules for when you&amp;rsquo;re out in Space.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Rules for character improvement that rewards you when you succeed and brings you down when you don&amp;rsquo;t.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Light bookkeeping Campaign and Economic systems that enhance the game instead of bogging it down.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Color paper character and space ship counters.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;And much more&amp;hellip;&amp;#10;&amp;#10;5150 Fringe Space is designed to be played solo or same side against the game mechanics, but also works just as well when played head to head against your friends.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Playable with any figures you may already have or just with the paper counters we&amp;rsquo;ve included. Play it any way you want, just play it!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
